      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project or a dedicated work horse? This vehicle has certainly lived a full life and shows significant wear and tear, but it still offers a great opportunity for someone looking to roll up their sleeves! It\u2019s a diamond in the rough that needs some serious TLC to get back to its best, making it the perfect choice for a mechanic's special or a parts car.",
