    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for those seeking a functional daily driver. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, a few small door dings, and some fading on the roof's clear coat. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows moderate wear and some minor staining consistent with regular use over the years. Mechanically, the car runs well and has been regularly serviced, though it may require some minor maintenance in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that offers practical transportation at an affordable price point.",
