    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that presents in showroom condition. This one-owner, garage-kept masterpiece retains its original deep-luster paint, free of any swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections. The interior is a time capsule, featuring pristine leather upholstery that still carries a factory-fresh scent, with zero wear on the bolsters or tactile surfaces. Every electronic feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium audio system, functions with precision. Under the hood, the engine bay is spotless, reflecting a rigorous maintenance schedule performed exclusively by certified technicians. The vehicle drives with the same tightness and responsiveness as the day it was delivered, complemented by a full set of service records and a clean title. This is a rare find for a discerning buyer seeking perfection without compromise.",
